item.title: CVE-2023-28066|2024-08-02T12:30:23.957Z -- dell -- dell%20os%20recovery%20tool
item.description: Dell OS Recovery Tool, versions 2.2.4013 and 2.3.7012.0, contain an Improper Access Control Vulnerability. A local authenticated non-administrator user could potentially exploit this vulnerability in order to elevate privileges on the system.
